## Project Workflow

1. Data Loading
2. Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
3. Data Cleaning
4. Feature Engineering (One-Hot Encoding)
5. Train-Test Split
6. Baseline Random Forest
7. Class Imbalance Handling (class-weighted training)
8. Hyperparameter Tuning (grid search over tree count & depth)
9. Cross-Validation (Accuracy & Recall, 5-fold)
10. ROC-AUC Evaluation
11. Feature Importance Analysis
12. Customer Segmentation using K-Means
13. Business Insights & Retention Strategy

