### Final Model Selection

Multiple combinations of tree count (`n_estimators`) and depth (`max_depth`) were evaluated against Accuracy, Recall, Precision, and F1-score. The final configuration was selected by balancing strong Recall (catching potential churners) against overall Accuracy and ROC-AUC, then validated using 5-fold cross-validation to confirm the results were stable across different data splits rather than a result of a single train-test split.

